# Dependencies
node_modules/
# package-lock.json is COMMITTED so Netlify uses deterministic `npm ci`.
# (Leaving it un-tracked made cloud builds run `npm install`, which re-resolved
#  ^ ranges and broke when a transitive dep published a bad version — Jul 2026.)

